== 历史和简介 ==
Interior Design由哈里·V·安德森（Harry V. Anderson）于1932年在[[紐約|紐約]][[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]创办。哈里·V·安德森也是该杂志的出版人和编辑，该杂志在[[二战|二战]]期间暂时停刊。战后哈里·V·安德森和惠特尼通訊公司（Whitney Communications Company）的{{link-en|约翰·海·惠特尼|John Hay Whitney}}重新创办了该杂志。1959年，惠特尼通訊公司成为Interior Design的唯一持有人。哈里·V·安德森則担任雜誌编辑和出版人至1969年<ref name=obi>{{cite news|title=Harry V. Anderson, 81, Ex-Magazine Publisher|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1983/08/17/obituaries/harry-v-anderson-81-ex-magazine-publisher.html|access-date=January 26, 2017|work=The New York Times|date=August 17, 1983|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202061855/http://www.nytimes.com/1983/08/17/obituaries/harry-v-anderson-81-ex-magazine-publisher.html}}</ref>。

1984年，Cahners出版公司（[[RELX集團|RELX集團]]的前身）从惠特尼通訊公司手中收購该杂志<ref>{{Cite news|author=Tony Silber|title=The Sale, Decline, and Ultimate Demise of Cahners Publishing|url=http://www.foliomag.com/the-sale-decline-and-ultimate-demise-of-cahners-publishing/|accessdate=January 26, 2017|work=Folio|date=March 29, 2016|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921023120/https://www.foliomag.com/the-sale-decline-and-ultimate-demise-of-cahners-publishing/}}</ref>。2010年3月，该杂志又被Sandow Media收購<ref>{{Cite news|title=Sandow Media Acquires Interior Design Magazine and Furniture Today|url=https://www.editoratlarge.com/news/sandow-media-acquires-interior-design-magazine-and-furniture-today|accessdate=January 26, 2017|work=Editor at Large|date=March 18, 2010|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202053909/https://www.editoratlarge.com/news/sandow-media-acquires-interior-design-magazine-and-furniture-today}}</ref>。

